      <title><![CDATA[前端开发环境搭建整理]]></title>
      <url>/2018/02/05/%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="一、安装NodeJS;">一、安装NodeJS<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1">[1]</a></sup>;</h4><p><a name="mac_os"></a><strong>Mac OS</strong><br>使用Homebrew<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn2" id="fnref2">[2]</a></sup>安装（<em>推荐</em>）：</p><ol><li><p>安装Homebrew；</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/usr/bin/ruby -e <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)</span>"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装NodeJS；</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">brew install node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><ul><li>使用安装包安装 | 下载地址：<a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v8.9.4/node-v8.9.4.pkg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>node-v8.9.4.pkg</em></a></li><li>Source Code 安装 <a href="#source_code_setup"><sup>[查看]</sup></a>;</li></ul><p><strong>Linux</strong></p><ul><li>使用编译好的文件 | <a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">前往</a></li><li><a name="source_code_setup"></a>Source Code 安装<ol><li><p><a href="https://nodejs.org/dist/v8.9.4/node-v8.9.4.tar.gz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">下载</a>Source Code 或 在 命令行中执行下面的命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl https://nodejs.org/dist/v8.9.4/node-v8.9.4.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>执行下面的命令进行安装；</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 解压压缩包</span></span><br><span class="line">tar -xzvf node-v8.9.4.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进入解压得到的目录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> node-v8.9.4</span><br><span class="line">./configure</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 这一步的时间会很长！</span></span><br><span class="line">make &amp;&amp; make install</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看当前安装的Node的版本 </span></span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol></li></ul><p><strong>Windows</strong> [略]</p><h4 id="二、安装常用工具">二、安装常用工具</h4><ul><li><p>Webpack</p><p>A. 全局安装<br><em>使用 yarn 安装：</em></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --global webpack</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>使用 npm 安装：</em></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --global webpack</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><link href="/css/katex.min.css" rel="stylesheet"><hr class="footnotes-sep"><section class="footnotes"><ol class="footnotes-list"><li class="footnote-item" id="fn1"><p>NodeJS官网：<a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/</a> <a href="#fnref1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li><li class="footnote-item" id="fn2"><p>Homebrew官网: <a href="https://brew.sh/index_zh-cn.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://brew.sh/index_zh-cn.html</a> <a href="#fnref2" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li></ol></section><!-- build time:Wed Feb 07 2018 11:51:22 GMT+0800 (CST) -->]]></content>
      
